      <title>英国福利削减了汽车制造商的电动汽车野心的意外风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/uk-welfare-cuts-pose-unexpected-risk-to-carmakers-ev-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将英国福利支出减少数十亿英镑的计划可能会产生意外的后果：破坏该国推动零排放车辆销售的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/uk-welfare-cuts-pose-unexpected-risk-to-carmakers-ev-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国说，随着美国关税织机的震惊，这已经为震惊做好了准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-says-it-s-prepared-for-greater-shocks-as-us-tariffs-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李·昆格（Li Qiang）表示，该国为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布下个月对其贸易伙伴宣布更多关税的世界准备“超出预期的冲击”做好了准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-says-it-s-prepared-for-greater-shocks-as-us-tariffs-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 02:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国脱欧英国放弃了成为全球交易警察的野心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-03-21/brexit-britain-abandons-ambition-to-be-global-deal-cop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国不再想成为全球反托拉斯十字军。改革可能会看到更少的交易被烘烤。这对银行家有好处，为律师而中等，为消费者担心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-03-21/brexit-britain-abandons-ambition-to-be-global-deal-cop</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
